{
  "page": "Holy Brotherhood of the Andals",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>Holy Brotherhood of the Andals</b> was an alliance of seven <a href=\"/index.php/Andal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal\">Andal</a> warlords and petty kings assembled during the <a href=\"/index.php/Andal_invasion\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal invasion\">Andal invasion</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">Stormlands</a> to fight against the <a href=\"/index.php/First_Men\" title=\"First Men\">First Men</a> and carve kingdoms for its members. King <a href=\"/index.php/Monfryd_V_Durrandon\" title=\"Monfryd V Durrandon\">Monfryd V Durrandon</a> defeated them at the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_Bronzegate\" title=\"Battle of Bronzegate\">Battle of Bronzegate</a> at the cost of his own life.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Holy_Brotherhood_of_the_Andals&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a>